EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.

   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16

2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2627/15.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 232100Z OCT 15.
